author: Katie Jerkovich
title: PHOTOS: Bella Hadid Shows Off Backside In Snaps From Jamaica
text:
TOP 5542033 
Bella Hadid showed her 11.5 million followers almost everything in a snap she shared on Sunday while on vacation in Jamaica. 
The 20-year-old Victoria’s Secret model posted the scandalous photo on Instagram of her on a bamboo bridge in a peach one-piece swimsuit. (RELATED: Bella Hadid Celebrates Her Birthday In Chain Mail Two-Piece Suit [PHOTOS]) Bella Hadid strikes a pose at the end of the runway. (Photo credit: Splash News) 
In the shot, the model had her back to the camera and showed off almost all of her backside in the revealing outfit. In the caption next to the post she did not write anything and only included several heart emojis and a peace emoji. 
A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 19, 2017 at 8:32pm PDT 
On Monday, she shared a photo in the same outfit while sitting on a bed. In the shot, she showed off part of her sideboob. The caption next to the post read, “Morning.” A post shared by Bella Hadid (@bellahadid) on Mar 20, 2017 at 9:58am PDT 
Hadid spent the weekend in the tropical location with friends soaking up the sun while hanging out in the water. She posted several of the photos on the site.
